data.description: Nestled in the scenic hills of Riverside in the neighborhood of La Sierra Acres, this charming property at 7083 Idyllwild Ln offers a perfect blend of comfort and serenity. This 11,761 sqft. lot family home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a well-appointed kitchen, and open living space.    Enjoy breathtaking views of the surrounding landscape from your kitchen window  The generously sized backyard provides ample space for outdoor entertainment and gardening enthusiasts. With its prime location near Hidden Valley Nature Center, Galleria at Tyler and 91 Fwy, this property combines tranquility with convenience, making it an ideal place to call home in Riverside. *Probate Sale, court confirmation required*
